This paper deals with the design of caching systems in computer networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also involves optimization problems and algorithms, which are relevant to the categories of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of caching policies on network security (cs.CR) and information theory (cs.IT).
